{
  "stem": "6526.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're not going towards Warsaw, but they're coming from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we're told that the agreement supposedly made is not the agreement, that they going up to Brest, Brest-Litovsk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So being that we were so close, and being that we were about 33 kilometers from our town, we heard what happened to Kaluszyn, that the town was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The center of town was all destroyed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People ran away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no place to live, this and that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we left in our home, my mother, my sister, and my grandmother, my grandma-- my father's mother-- in the house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we wanted to go to out to see what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came to our town, we couldn't get into our house, because strange people were living there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because everything was destroyed, they had to find some places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow we got in there, and we had to get the people out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we hired horses and buggies, horses and wagons, to take the people to other places.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some had relatives in another town, and so we paid-- we paid them to go out, and we paid their transportation to leave the house back to us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we took in some relatives that were burned out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is how we remained in Kaluszyn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother, they were in-- they took all the-- most of the Jews took into church.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The church was a large church in there, because they had to keep them-- to save the population, the Germans want to save the population and fight only the military, because they took-- and being in the church, they were all afraid that this is what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're going to bomb the church and everybody in it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this didn't happen, thank God.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
